    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818660/extras/0bacb9ed3cac78bd1236b275063938e6.avif?t=1769572065\" width=600 height=596 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款第三人称角色扮演游戏中，扮演吸血鬼大战四方，同时探索黑暗奇幻背景下的开放世界。做出影响人类福祉——或是你自己的选择；强化你的吸血鬼技能，对抗强盗、巨魔和不死生物； 并在香艳的全动态场景中自娱自乐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818660/extras/544185215ffa05fed1670622af239352.avif?t=1769572065\" width=600 height=144 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你扮演首位吸血鬼——卡利斯卡·卡恩斯坦，在过去的几千年创造并控制了一支吸血鬼军队。她的手下担心她会安于现状，很快就有了祸心，最后造就了一场致命的背叛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从千年沉睡中醒来后，茫然的卡利斯卡形单影只，独自踏上了重建大军的旅程，同时还要追杀让她陷入沉睡的罪魁祸首。作为卡利斯卡，你必须与女术士、兽人和人类结盟，和他们并肩作战，夺回你一度拥有的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818660/extras/dd6420bbd5b8a4f17f0ab9cef21bedc1.avif?t=1769572065\" width=600 height=144 /></span>我们的目标是制作一款能让人愉快游玩的游戏，让精心打磨、品味非凡的浪漫场景无缝衔接游戏玩法和剧情。开放世界区域和游戏系统正在开发中，目前游戏里只有几个任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >值得期待的内容：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  • 动态的战斗风格</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  • 全配音任务</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  • 角色自定义</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  • 升级和属性点系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  • 偷袭敌人，咬住他们的脖子喝血！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  • 游戏过程和过场动画中的诱人邂逅</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  • 探索世界和地牢可以发现一系列服装</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  • 单手和双手战斗风格，包括剑在内的各种武器</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818660/extras/367bafc03be00a1a64c7d7118bb7843d.poster.avif?t=1769572065\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818660/extras/367bafc03be00a1a64c7d7118bb7843d.webm?t=1769572065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818660/extras/367bafc03be00a1a64c7d7118bb7843d.mp4?t=1769572065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818660/extras/539eacd358c3c348a337bc0dfaab2865.poster.avif?t=1769572065\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818660/extras/539eacd358c3c348a337bc0dfaab2865.webm?t=1769572065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818660/extras/539eacd358c3c348a337bc0dfaab2865.mp4?t=1769572065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818660/extras/dc5a56c4012c1c38d7f4ab0f53ded683.poster.avif?t=1769572065\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818660/extras/dc5a56c4012c1c38d7f4ab0f53ded683.webm?t=1769572065\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818660/extras/dc5a56c4012c1c38d7f4ab0f53ded683.mp4?t=1769572065\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1818660/extras/4b4b2b87ab8537d2dcfd6afbf459b2b5.poster.avif?t=1769572065\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.co